=====================================================

Business Goal

Every AI recommendation within ORIP should be explainable.

The objective is to help analysts, managers, auditors and regulators understand why a recommendation was made and what evidence was used.

This feature should be available throughout the platform.

=====================================================

Add an "Explain Why" icon beside every AI recommendation.

Examples include

- BIA questionnaire recommendations
- BCP document changes
- Crisis exercise recommendations
- Governance response suggestions
- Redaction decisions
- AI generated summaries
- Business impact analysis
- Executive insights

